x4freetext: The targets used in the study of the 10B(t,p)12B
reaction and the 10B(t,d)11B reaction were prepared by
mu-m nicel foils.The targets used in the study of the
elastic scattering cross section and the 10B(t,alpha)
9Be reactions were thin self-supporting foils of 10B.
These 10B foils were produced by a procedure which is
very similar to that commonly used to make carbon foils
